Job responsibilities:
Design web pages for corporate branding and work on interface solutions
Support senior designers to create and convey design solutions
Analysis and improvement for the design projects (wireframe, mockup and prototype)
Design for the advertising material and relevant graphics when needed
Handle ad-hoc tasks or projects as assigned
