Qualification

Diploma or above in multimedia or graphic design;
1-2 year working experience or above in graphic design/ web design/ advertising (experience in online or fashion industry is a plus);
Proficiency in In Adobe Creative Suite (Photoshop, Illustrator) etc.;
Detail-minded and creative;
Ability to understand and handle tasks independently ;

Benefits:

5-day work week
Medical insurance & dental care
Public Holiday
12 – 17 days paid Annual Leave
5 days Marriage Leave
Birthday Leave
Staff purchase discount

Interested parties, please press "Apply Now".
